Author: sadbottomthrowaway
Text: oh dear, i completely didn’t even think about that. i’ll delete it. not my intention at all! i was just having a body dysmorphia moment and was hoping to gain some clarity on what other people might see my bmi as.

Author: DogTeeth_Val
Text: Hi, I don't want to be *that* girl, but I don't think this post is a good idea. A bunch of us hearing that they're in the fat range could potentially be triggered into indulging in disordered behaviour.
